---
layout: layouts/inner.njk
title: Contact
permalink: /contact/
eyebrow:
  en: Contact
  vi: Liên hệ
  zh: 联系我们
heading:
  en: Let's Grow the Future Together.
  vi: Cùng kiến tạo tương lai bền vững.
  zh: 携手共创可持续未来。
lead:
  en: Tell us about partnership, products, logistics or careers — we will route your message to the right team.
  vi: Cho chúng tôi biết về hợp tác, sản phẩm, logistics hoặc tuyển dụng — chúng tôi sẽ chuyển đến đúng bộ phận.
  zh: 告诉我们您的合作、产品、物流或招聘需求——我们会转交对应团队。
---

<div class="contact-page">
  <div class="contact-page__info">
    <p><strong>{{ site.emailPartner }}</strong></p>
    <p><a href="tel:{{ site.phoneTel }}">{{ site.phone }}</a></p>
    <p>
      <span class="lang en">{{ site.address.en }}</span>
      <span class="lang vi">{{ site.address.vi }}</span>
      <span class="lang zh">{{ site.address.zh }}</span>
    </p>
    <div class="contact-page__map" aria-hidden="true">
      <iframe title="Map" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"
        src="https://maps.google.com/maps?q=Ho%20Chi%20Minh%20City&t=&z=12&ie=UTF8&iwloc=&output=embed"></iframe>
    </div>
  </div>
  {% set productCode = "" %}
  {% include "partials/contact-form.njk" %}
</div>
